      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong>&nbsp;pasta</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>sauce</strong>&nbsp;to 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> individual <strong>oven-proof dishes</strong> (or one big one!) and top with the <strong>meatballs</strong> and <strong>grated cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the dish<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> in the oven for 10-15 min or until the<strong> cheese</strong>&nbsp;has melted and the <strong>meatballs</strong> are cooked through</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>dijon mustard</strong> and <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt&nbsp;</strong>- this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
